    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/list/?60_1.html">潍博之益</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?60_1.html">志愿者活动</a></div>
      <span>志愿者活动</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">文化潍坊·志愿有我——12.4国际博物馆日主题活动</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p style="text-indent: 384px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877472564926206.jpg" title="图片1.jpg" alt="图片1.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 384px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 21px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; text-align: left;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">12月4日，为迎接第31个“国际志愿者日”，进一步深化社会主义核心价值观教育，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(43,43,43);font-size:19px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family:宋体">弘扬</span>“奉献、友爱、互助、进步”的志愿精神，引导广大志愿者积极参与到弘扬中国传统文化中来，推动全市志愿服务事业不断发展，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">潍坊市博物馆与共青团潍坊市委、潍坊市志愿者协会、潍坊市朗诵与语言艺术协会联合社会各界人士在潍坊市博物馆一楼大厅举办了</span>“文化潍坊·志愿有我”的主题庆祝活动。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877472984857542.jpg" title="图片2.jpg" alt="图片2.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">志愿者们集体合影</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877473171856626.jpg" title="图片3.jpg" alt="图片3.jpg" width="514" height="374" style="width: 514px; height: 374px;"/></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">潍博志愿者</span>——潍坊学院弘德国学社同学们的合影</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877473803280317.jpg" title="图片4.jpg" alt="图片4.jpg" width="522" height="351" style="width: 522px; height: 351px;"/></p><p style="text-indent:56px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 潍博志愿者</span>——潍坊学院历史与旅游学院同学们的合影</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877474218127485.jpg" title="图片5.jpg" alt="图片5.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 潍博志愿者</span>——潍坊学院机电与车辆工程学院同学们的合影</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877474596515241.jpg" title="图片6.jpg" alt="图片6.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 潍博志愿者</span>——山东科技职业学院建筑工程系同学们的合影</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">来自潍坊学院、山东科技职业学院、山东海事职业学院、山东交通职业学院的</span>8支潍博志愿者代表队与社会各界爱心人士2000余人参加了此次活动。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877474996888777.jpg" title="图片7.jpg" alt="图片7.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">共青团潍坊市委志愿者工作部部长</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">缪晶晶致辞</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">共青团潍坊市委志愿者工作部部长缪晶晶</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、潍坊市博物馆馆长吉树春、山东海事职业学院副书记徐立清，潍坊市志愿者代表王晓春，分别发表了热情洋溢的讲话，对志愿者的奉献精神和爱心行动给予了充分肯定和鼓励。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877475285962080.jpg" title="图片8.jpg" alt="图片8.jpg" width="509" height="287" style="width: 509px; height: 287px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;担任宣誓仪式的四位旗手</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877475525647871.jpg" title="图片9.jpg" alt="图片9.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">全体志愿者集体宣誓仪式</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">随后，全体志愿者进行了集体宣誓仪式。</span>“我愿意成为一名光荣的志愿者。我承诺：尽已所能，不计报酬，帮助他人，服务社会。实行志愿精神，传播先进文化，为建设团结互助、平等友爱、共同前进的美好社会贡献力量”的誓词铿锵有力、感染人心。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877475937009489.jpg" title="图片10.jpg" alt="图片10.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">小小讲解员和家长共同参与亲子活动环节</span>——传统礼仪展示</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877476236819975.jpg" title="图片11.jpg" alt="图片11.jpg" width="538" height="371" style="width: 538px; height: 371px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;潍博志愿者来自山东科技职业学员的同学带来了精彩的古典器乐展示</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; text-indent: 35px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877476608441008.jpg" title="图片12.jpg" alt="图片12.jpg" width="545" height="358" style="width: 545px; height: 358px;"/></p><p style="text-indent:47px;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">社会志愿者原创集体诗朗诵《志愿服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">爱的奉献</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">》</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877477374266202.jpg" title="图片13.jpg" alt="图片13.jpg" width="554" height="317" style="width: 554px; height: 317px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">海事职业学院志愿者汉服表演</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877477749857695.jpg" title="图片14.jpg" alt="图片14.jpg" width="571" height="309" style="width: 571px; height: 309px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;潍坊学院数学系的志愿者手语表演《有你的地方就是天堂》</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877478097929045.jpg" title="图片15.jpg" alt="图片15.jpg" width="567" height="333" style="width: 567px; height: 333px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">古代男子作揖礼互动展示</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877478641170118.jpg" title="图片16.jpg" alt="图片16.jpg"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">古代女子万福礼互动展示</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">此次活动中，志愿者们通过精彩的文化知识问答、汉服走秀、传统礼仪展示、古典器乐演奏、手语舞蹈、诗朗诵等活动，既展现了当代志愿者的别样风采，又让现场的观众接受了一场中国传统文化的洗礼。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/upload/image/20170222/14877478917447157.jpg" title="图片17.jpg" alt="图片17.jpg" width="488" height="308" style="width: 488px; height: 308px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 28px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">作为此次活动主办方之一的潍坊市博物馆，最近几年，高度重视志愿者服务建设，通过与潍坊学院、山东科技职业学院等各大院校积极合作，让更多的优秀大学生加入到了志愿者行列。同时，放宽志愿者年龄限制，积极招募文化水平高、热心公益事业的退休老干部、老专家，不断提高志愿者队伍的层次。潍博志愿者队伍由原来的不足百人，发展到现在</span>1800<span style="font-family:宋体">多人，志愿者讲解员</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">133</span><span style="font-family:宋体">人、小小讲解员</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">32</span><span style="font-family:宋体">人，数量翻了十几番，志愿服务水平也得到极大提高。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">此次活动的举办，对于潍坊市博物馆乃至全市的志愿服务建设都将起到积极地推动作用，也将为文化潍坊、魅力潍博的建设注入新的活力。</span></span></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=495"></script></div>
      
